OL,3,CNumber of police officers injured in
OL,4,CRotherham riot rises to 51
OL,6,FPolice say the number of officers
OL,7,Fconfirmed as injured as a result of a
OL,8,Friot outside a hotel in Rotherham has
OL,9,Fmore than quadrupled to 51.
OL,11,FOfficers received injuries such as
OL,12,Fbroken bones, concussion, bruising,
OL,13,Fand head wounds after concrete blocks,
OL,14,Fchairs, tree branches and fire
OL,15,Fextinguishers were thrown at them
OL,16,Fduring the violent scenes outside the
OL,17,FHoliday Inn Express in Wath-upon-
OL,18,FDearne on Sunday.
OL,20,FOriginally the force had estimated 12
OL,21,Fofficers had been injured.
