OL,6,FHorses and dogs were also hurt, with
OL,7,Fone horse being forced to retire from
OL,8,Fduty after its hoof was injured.
OL,10,FThose officers unable to resume
OL,11,Ffrontline duties are now helping to
OL,12,Ftrawl through CCTV to gather evidence
OL,13,Fto secure arrests.
