OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable David
OL,7,FHartley said: "I am so proud of our
OL,8,Fofficers' bravery and resilience on
OL,9,Fthe night and now their ongoing
OL,10,Fdedication to helping our communities
OL,11,Fremain safe, coming back to work
OL,12,Fdespite being subjected to such
OL,13,Fterrible levels of violence.
