OL,6,F"Please be assured, we are continuing
OL,7,Four work to identify and arrest the
OL,8,Foffenders at pace. If you were
OL,9,Finvolved in the outright acts of
OL,10,Fviolence and thuggery on Sunday, let
OL,11,Fme be clear - we are coming for you.
OL,12,FWe are determined to be arresting each
OL,13,Fand every one of the offenders from
OL,14,Ftheir homes in the coming days."
